        "startram_contracts.go follows the same default-only metadata pattern, so contract evolution policy is not locally expressed where contracts are defined."
      ],
      "suggestion": "Introduce an explicit contract lifecycle declaration convention in the contract files (for example, required per-entry compatibility/lifecycle fields and optional deprecation metadata), and add a CI assertion that rejects new/changed contracts without explicit lifecycle metadata.",
