        "README.md governance emphasizes typed contract APIs for protocol/error surfaces, but exported raw message constants permit downstream callers to depend directly on text-level semantics."
      ],
      "suggestion": "Make message text non-exported (or expose only typed accessors tied to ContractID), and require cross-module consumers to resolve messages through contract descriptors/accessor functions rather than importing string constants.",
